## 1. Overview

This Privacy Policy explains how D3MONIC (“Bot”) collects, uses, and stores data in compliance with:

* Discord Developer Terms
* Hypixel API policies

---

## 2. Data We Collect

### a) Discord Data

* User ID
* Username & discriminator
* Server ID
* Roles (for permission checks)

### b) Minecraft / Hypixel Data

* UUID
* In-game name
* Public stats (Bedwars, guild, etc.)
* Social media links (if publicly linked on Hypixel)

### c) Verification Data

* Discord ID ↔ Minecraft UUID mapping

---

## 3. How We Use Data

We use collected data to:

* Provide bot features (stats, verification, leaderboards)
* Link Discord accounts to Minecraft accounts
* Run giveaways and assign roles
* Improve functionality and performance

We DO NOT:

* Sell user data
* Share private data with third parties

---

## 4. Data Storage

* Data may be stored in databases (e.g., MongoDB)
* Stored securely and only accessible by the bot owner
* Some data is temporary (API responses)

---

## 5. Data Retention

We retain data:

* As long as necessary for functionality
* Until a user requests removal
* Or until the bot is discontinued

---

## 6. User Rights

You may:

* Request removal of your data
* Stop using the Bot at any time

To request deletion, contact the bot owner.

---

## 7. Third-Party Services

This Bot uses:

* Discord API → https://discord.com/terms
* Hypixel API → https://api.hypixel.net/

We are not responsible for how these services handle data.

---

## 8. Security

We take reasonable measures to:

* Protect stored data
* Prevent unauthorized access

However, no system is 100% secure.

---

